data.text: Bigg Boss is one of the most popular reality shows. Several contestants of the show have appeared in Salman Khan's films. Read on. Submitted by TellychakkarTeam on Mon, 05/03/2021 - 17:50 About Author Submitted by TellychakkarTeam on Mon, 05/03/2021 - 17:50 Submitted by TellychakkarTeam on Thu, 07/02/2015 - 16:58 About Author Submitted by TellychakkarTeam on Thu, 07/02/2015 - 16:58 Submitted by TellychakkarTeam on Wed, 07/02/2014 - 19:18 About Author Submitted by TellychakkarTeam on Wed, 07/02/2014 - 19:18 Submitted by TellychakkarTeam on Sat, 01/25/2014 - 13:34 About Author Submitted by TellychakkarTeam on Sat, 01/25/2014 - 13:34 Submitted by TellychakkarTeam on Tue, 07/02/2013 - 17:52 About Author Submitted by TellychakkarTeam on Tue, 07/02/2013 - 17:52 Colors’ Nautanki- The Comedy Theater has been leaving no stones unturned to entertain audiences. Tellychakkar.com earlier reported about Kai Po Che! team making an appearance and Imam turning into a planet. And the fun will continue in the coming episodes. Now, Jackky Bhagnani will also be seen in the show promoting his upcoming flick Rangrezz. In fact, he will also throw in a dance performance. Submitted by TellychakkarTeam on Mon, 02/18/2013 - 15:41 About Author Submitted by TellychakkarTeam on Mon, 02/18/2013 - 15:41 Latest Bigg Boss evictee Aashka Goradia is very hurt at the way her image and sexuality was distorted during her stay in the Lonavala house. Talking to the media, she shared, "That one single picture of me and Sana Khan has destroyed the goodwill I have built over 12 long years of hard work in the TV industry. You guys know me well; have you ever seen any dirty controversy about me.” Submitted by TellychakkarTeam on Wed, 01/02/2013 - 16:53 About Author Submitted by TellychakkarTeam on Wed, 01/02/2013 - 16:53 Nobody knew television actor Santosh Shukla till he entered the Bigg Boss house this season. But, today he is a household name, thanks to his flirtatious nature and his incomplete love story with Aashka Goradia and Karishma Kotak. We spoke to this very man about his exit from the house and his future plans. Excerpts: Submitted by TellychakkarTeam on Mon, 12/17/2012 - 18:53 About Author Submitted by TellychakkarTeam on Mon, 12/17/2012 - 18:53 We saw Dinesh lala Yadav aka Nirahua moving out of the Bigg Boss 6 House on 12 December 2012 in the mid-week elimination and now it’s Santosh Shukla.
